# HEYDAY client

- Pages in `client/src/pages/`; feature components in `client/src/components/`
- Wrap authenticated screens in `ProtectedRoute`; use `DashboardLayout` for app shell
- Shared: `Icon` (Material Symbols), `DateText`, `format.js` helpers
- Task calendar labels: `displayTaskTitle()` from `client/src/utils/taskDisplay.js` (nickname || title)
- Calendar grids: `.calendar-grid` in `index.css` — `grid-template-columns: repeat(7, 1fr)`; header row must also be 7 columns (`grid-cols-7`)
- Avoid `overflow-hidden` on calendar wrapper if it clips the Saturday column

Add new routes in `App.jsx` and nav in `Sidebar.jsx` when creating pages.

## Sidebar (2026-06-15)

- `SidebarContext` — `collapsed`, `toggleCollapsed`, `sidebarWidth` (260 | 72); `sidebar-collapsed-v1` in localStorage
- `DashboardLayout` — `style={{ marginLeft: sidebarWidth }}` with transition; do not hardcode `ml-[260px]`
- Task Hub `NavLink` has `end={taskHub}` so `/tasks/:userId` only highlights “My tasks”
- Footer: compact user + small logout; collapsed = avatar + icon logout

## Checklist editor (`ChecklistEditor.jsx`)

- Task card: textarea full title, nickname input, default assignee select, timing row (days / when / anchor)
- Timing grid: `sm:grid-cols-12` — nickname 3, assignee 3, days 1, when 2, anchor 3
- Save sends `calendar_nickname` + `default_role` to checklists API

## Marketing calendar

- `MarketingDayEvents` section order: Social → Tasks → Milestones
- `fridayCelebrationFetchEnd` / `partitionFridayCelebrations` in `calendarUtils.js` for toolbar popover
- `MonthBirthdaysModal` — pin CRM birthdays per month; add birthday via CRM search + `PATCH /api/crm/:id`
- Double-click day cell (empty area) → new post modal; chips stop propagation on buttons/links only
- Marketing page wrapper: `select-none` with `[&_input]:select-text` exception
